Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:33.80,Chn,,0,0,0,,最近怎么样? Hey.\N{\rEng}What's going on? Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:38.42,Chn,,0,0,0,,Oh 耶 嘿 有空吗? 最近怎么样?\N{\rEng}Oh yeah, hey, whassup? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:40.90,Chn,,0,0,0,,帅.\N{\rEng}Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:51.66,Chn,,0,0,0,,嘿, 最近怎么样? - 嘿 Clyde.\N{\rEng}Hey, what's going on? - Hey Clyde.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:53.21,Chn,,0,0,0,,嘿.\N{\rEng}- Hi Clyde. Hey. - Hi Clyde.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:54.64,Chn,,0,0,0,,最近怎么样?\N{\rEng}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:07:58.96,Chn,,0,0,0,,嘿 丑八怪!\N{\rEng}Hey ugly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:09.40,Chn,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kyle. 其实,别人怎么看你 根本无所谓 , 对吧?\N{\rEng}Hey, Kyle. Look man, it doesn't matter what people think, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:14.40,Chn,,0,0,0,,亚伯拉罕·林肯也很丑 可是你看他的成就\N{\rEng}You know, Abraham Lincoln was pretty ugly too, but look what he accomplished.
